headline: November Sustainability Portfolio: Latest Issue Features Global Leaders and Breakthrough Climate Insights
summary: BizClik has released the latest editions in its Sustainability portfolio, marking the completion of the November 2025 series. The 60th issue of Sustainability Magazine highlights global leaders, emerging technologies, and the strategies shaping the future of climate action.
